-- UniCredit’s Rampl Likely to Remain Chairman, Messaggero Reports
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2010-11-04T07:04:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/unicredit-s-rampl-likely-to-remain-chairman-messaggero-reports.html
UniCredit SpA  Chairman  Dieter Rampl 
probably will keep his position at Italy’s largest bank after
reaching an agreement with investors, daily Il Messaggero
reported.  “Rampl is an excellent chairman,” Il Messaggero cited
Deputy Chairman  Vincenzo Calandra  as saying yesterday. Rampl
still could leave the bank before the end of his term in 2012,
Il Messaggero reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Armorel Kenna  in Milan at 
